CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1772395908
OL,3,C'WRU's Julius Caesar? Never
OL,4,Cunderestimate Welsh rugby's penchant
OL,5,Cfor mayhem'
OL,7,FThe late Roman General's views on
OL,8,Fwhether Welsh rugby should reduce from
OL,9,Ffour to three professional clubs were
OL,10,Fnever sought, even if he did know a
OL,11,Fthing or two about political unrest.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1772395908
OL,3,C'WRU's Julius Caesar? Never
OL,4,Cunderestimate Welsh rugby's penchant
OL,5,Cfor mayhem'
OL,7,FWelsh rugby might be a long way from
OL,8,FAncient Rome. Yet as Richard Collier-
OL,9,FKeywood faces a vote of no confidence
OL,10,Famid fury over governance reform and
OL,11,Fthe future of the professional game -
OL,12,Fincluding the proposed reduction of
OL,13,Fregions that could see the Ospreys
OL,14,Fcease to exist - the same question
OL,15,Flingers: Is this a reckoning for the
OL,16,Fleader or the direction of travel?
OL,18,FBecause history tells us that stopping
OL,19,Fthe person at the top doesn't always
OL,20,Fstop the movement.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1772395908
OL,3,C'WRU's Julius Caesar? Never
OL,4,Cunderestimate Welsh rugby's penchant
OL,5,Cfor mayhem'
OL,7,FIn the coming weeks, WRU Chair Collier-
OL,8,FKeywood will face a vote of no
OL,9,Fconfidence. If there is hope that
OL,10,Fousting him will salvage Welsh rugby's
OL,11,Fstatus quo, it is likely misguided.
OL,13,FEven if the chair is removed, the
OL,14,Freforms are likely to endure because
OL,15,Fthey have the support of the wider WRU
OL,16,Fgovernance structure, not just one man.
OL,18,FIt is a point that was repeated during
OL,19,Fthe WRU's audience with MSs at the
OL,20,FSenedd on Thursday.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1772395908
OL,3,C'WRU's Julius Caesar? Never
OL,4,Cunderestimate Welsh rugby's penchant
OL,5,Cfor mayhem'
OL,7,FThe reforms of professional rugby in
OL,8,FWales were devised by the WRU's
OL,9,Fexecutive team, led by CEO Abi Tierney
OL,10,Fand Director of Rugby Dave Reddin.
OL,12,FThey were then ratified unanimously by
OL,13,Fthe WRU's 12-person Board, which
OL,14,Fincludes Independent Non-Executive
OL,15,FDirectors, figures from the Community
OL,16,FGame and modern elite men's rugby
OL,17,Fexperience in the form of Jamie
OL,18,FRoberts.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1772395908
OL,3,C'WRU's Julius Caesar? Never
OL,4,Cunderestimate Welsh rugby's penchant
OL,5,Cfor mayhem'
OL,7,FIt will take over 50% of the vote
OL,8,Fshare to remove Collier-Keywood at the
OL,9,FEGM - which must take place before
OL,10,FApril 12. But it will take a lot more
OL,11,Fto reverse this.
OL,13,FIt is almost unfathomable that a new
OL,14,FChair would come in and detonate a
OL,15,Fproposal that has already been adopted
OL,16,Fwith so much internal support.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1772395908
OL,3,C'WRU's Julius Caesar? Never
OL,4,Cunderestimate Welsh rugby's penchant
OL,5,Cfor mayhem'
OL,7,FIf we stray into hypothetical
OL,8,Fsituations, that's where things could
OL,9,Fstart to turn. Were Collier-Keywood to
OL,10,Fgo, we don't know how his lieutenants
OL,11,Fwould react.
OL,13,FA new Chair may well want their own
OL,14,FCEO. Tierney may well make that
OL,15,Fdecision on her own.
OL,17,FAnd what would Reddin make of it all?
OL,18,FHe has been in post for less than a
OL,19,Fyear but has quickly become a pariah
OL,20,Fin the eyes of his detractors.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1772395908
OL,3,C'WRU's Julius Caesar? Never
OL,4,Cunderestimate Welsh rugby's penchant
OL,5,Cfor mayhem'
OL,7,FAll three have endured personal abuse
OL,8,Fin recent months - and a line has been
OL,9,Fcrossed in that regard. But their
OL,10,Fappetite for this process may wane. If
OL,11,Fthe Chair goes, others could decide to
OL,12,Ffollow.
OL,14,FAnd if Reddin, the real architect of
OL,15,Fthese plans, leaves, then the pressure
OL,16,Fto abandon them altogether might be
OL,17,Ftoo much for the WRU to bear.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1772395908
OL,3,C'WRU's Julius Caesar? Never
OL,4,Cunderestimate Welsh rugby's penchant
OL,5,Cfor mayhem'
OL,7,FBut even in that scenario, danger
OL,8,Fwould linger. How would Y11 react? The
OL,9,FOspreys owners have placed the Swansea-
OL,10,Fbased region in peril by also entering
OL,11,Fnegotiations to take over Cardiff.
OL,13,FIf Welsh rugby's governance structure
OL,14,Fcollapses, they may decide the chaos
OL,15,Fis too much and walk away from the
OL,16,Fgame altogether, taking their money
OL,17,Felsewhere, leaving two clubs in dire
OL,18,Fstraits.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1772395908
OL,3,C'WRU's Julius Caesar? Never
OL,4,Cunderestimate Welsh rugby's penchant
OL,5,Cfor mayhem'
OL,7,FThis is all hypothetical and it is a
OL,8,Fchain of events that is almost too
OL,9,Fcombustible to fathom. But you should
OL,10,Fnever underestimate Welsh rugby's
OL,11,Fpenchant for mayhem.
OL,13,FFor now it appears that the Union is
OL,14,Fnot backing down. Their visit to the
OL,15,FSenedd represented a tone shift. There
OL,16,Fwas less deference in their answers to
OL,17,Fpoliticians this time, they were more
OL,18,Funapologetic.
OL,20,FThey were digging their heels in, not
OL,21,Fconceding ground.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1772395908
OL,3,C'WRU's Julius Caesar? Never
OL,4,Cunderestimate Welsh rugby's penchant
OL,5,Cfor mayhem'
OL,7,FBut opponents to these plans can also
OL,8,Fturn to history for solace.
OL,10,FWhilst Caesar's ideologies endured
OL,11,Fafter his death, they did not last
OL,12,Fforever.
OL,14,FEven the Roman Empire fell, eventually.
OL,16,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV Wales, sent direct
OL,19,Fto your inbox every Saturday morning.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/11
